featured_reviews.review_id:
Oldest and main big mosques of the city.
Situated at central area of town.
Well equipped with all modern amenities like ac , water heaters , wash rooms, guest rooms , parking area, and many mores.
Also many shops are there in the mosque campus , selling books of Islamic verses and literature of all Arabic , Persian and Urdu.
Mats for recites namazs , agarbatti, tasbeeh
Watches attar and all Islamic goods.
Also in the festival like Eid and eidulzoha
lachha sewai and all variety of sewai sold here.
Visits once you can feel these things.
And above all the office of Anjuman Islamia is also there.
